{"tid":762293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒：阿里巴巴和京東已擱置發行ＣＤＲ","createTime":"2018-07-31T06:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T15:13:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3431ffeb753c4b3109b8b35e62d39001eabfbcc","tid":762293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280731839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280731839&d=1InRUhZWaBoppC7aDIOFyWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7e19bd1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280731839</a><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社３１日專訊》據《華爾街日報》報道，中國政府６月推行ＣＤＲ，意圖吸引新經濟企業到Ａ股市場作第二上市，但監管機構對此的熱情已極速降溫。報道引述知情人士稱，阿里巴巴和京東均已擱置發行ＣＤＲ的計劃，而相關官員們亦擔心股市疲軟，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無力吸收如此大規模的股票發行，進一步吸乾Ａ股市場資金流動性。</span></span>（ｅｙ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話取代香港？<br />\n<br />\n無香港比你吸錢 (吸港豬錢), 一早支爆左 9 世啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a609a0abebf28dba5d4e124d4025790476948a","tid":762293,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"發嚟香港啦，有港豬幫你埋單"},{"pid":"4460ac029c68d55cc87f412c4a6e4adcefd3375a","tid":762293,"uid":12021,"